ng static\ncorrelation effects and states with multipleexcitation character, such as the\ndissociating H2 molecule. Theseresults highlight the utility of long-range\ninteracting referencesystems as a starting point for the calculation of\nexcitation energiesand are of interest for developing and analyzing practical\napproximaterange-separated density-functional methodologies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Dec 2014 08:43:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-12-15"}
